'''Basic Korean Dictionary''' ({{Korean|hangul=한국어기초사전|hanja=韓國語基礎辭典|rr=hangugeo gicho sajeon|mr=han'gugǒ kich'o sajǒn}}) is an [[online dictionary|online]] [[learner's dictionary]] of the [[Korean language]], launched on 5 October 2016 by the [[National Institute of Korean Language]].<ref name="NIKL">{{Cite web|title=발자취|url=http://www.korean.go.kr/front/page/pageView.do?page_id=P000166&mn_id=74|website=[[National Institute of Korean Language]]|accessdate=11 June 2017}}</ref> It consists of one [[monolingual learner's dictionary|monolingual]] and ten [[bilingual dictionary|bilingual dictionaries]] that provide meanings of Korean words and expressions in Korean, [[English language|English]], [[Arabic]], [[French language|French]], [[Indonesian language|Indonesian]], [[Japanese language|Japanese]], [[Mongolian language|Mongolian]], [[Russian language|Russian]], [[Spanish language|Spanish]], [[Thai language|Thai]], and [[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]].

== Multilingual support ==
* Korean: Basic Korean dictionary
* Korean–English: Korean–English Learners' Dictionary
* Korean–Arabic: {{lang|ar|قاموس تعليم اللغة الكورية والعربية}}
* Korean–French: {{lang|fr|Dictionnaire d'apprentissage coréen–français}}
* Korean–Indonesian: {{lang|id|Kamus Pelajaran Bahasa Korea–Bahasa Indonesia}}
* Korean–Japanese: {{lang|ja|韓国語–日本語学習辞典}}
* Korean–Mongolian: {{lang|mn|Солонгос–Монгол сургалтын толь бичиг}}
* Korean–Russian: {{lang|ru|Корейско–русский учебный словарь}}
* Korean–Spanish: {{lang|es|Diccionario Didáctico Coreano–Español}}
* Korean–Thai: {{lang|th|พจนานุกรมสำหรับผู้เรียนภาษาเกาหลี–ไทย}}
* Korean–Vietnamese: {{lang|vi|Từ điển học tiếng Hàn–tiếng Việt của}}

