The '''''Bug Man''''' series is a crime/thriller novel series written by [[Tim Downs]] and published by [[Howard Books|Howard Publishing]]. Its protagonist Nick Polchak is a [[forensic entomologist]]. There are currently six novels in the series:

* ''Shoofly Pie'', 2003
* ''Chop Shop'', 2004
* ''First the Dead'', 2008
* ''Less than Dead'', 2009
* ''Ends of the Earth'', 2009–10
* ''Nick of Time'', 2011

The first two novels were major hits in the Christian Fiction market, and were combined into a collection in 2009.

